{"sort":28,"title":" 6 . 写一个方法去掉字符串中的空格","slug":"interview/8d5ea4ab3d","date":"2020-08-11T00:00:00.000Z","updated":"2021-06-17T11:25:09.047Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/interview/8d5ea4ab3d.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"描述写一个方法去掉字符串中的空格，要求传入不同的类型分别能去掉前、后、前后、中间的空格 ","covers":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"描述\"><a href=\"#描述\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"描述\"></a>描述</h2><p>写一个方法去掉字符串中的空格，要求传入不同的类型分别能去掉前、后、前后、中间的空格 </p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h2 id=\"解答\"><a href=\"#解答\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解答\"></a>解答</h2><pre><code class=\"hljs js\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> str = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;  s t  r  &quot;</span>;\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> POSITION = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Object</span>.freeze(&#123;\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">left</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Symbol</span>(),\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">right</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Symbol</span>(),\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">both</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Symbol</span>(),\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">center</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Symbol</span>(),\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">all</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Symbol</span>()\n&#125;);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">trim</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">str, position = POSITION.both</span>) </span>&#123;\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (!!POSITION[position]) <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">throw</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Error</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;unexpected position value&quot;</span>);\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">switch</span> (position) &#123;\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">case</span> POSITION.left:\n            str = str.replace(<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/^\\s+/</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&quot;</span>);\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>;\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">case</span> POSITION.right:\n            str = str.replace(<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/\\s+$/</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&quot;</span>);\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>;\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">case</span> POSITION.both:\n            str = str.replace(<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/^\\s+/</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&quot;</span>).replace(<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/\\s+$/</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&quot;</span>);\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>;\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">case</span> POSITION.center:\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">while</span> (str.match(<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/\\w\\s+\\w/</span>)) &#123;\n                str = str.replace(<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/(\\w)(\\s+)(\\w)/</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">`$1$3`</span>);\n            &#125;\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>;\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">case</span> POSITION.all:\n            str = str.replace(<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/\\s/g</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&quot;</span>);\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>;\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span>:\n    &#125;\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> str;\n&#125;\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> result = trim(str);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`|<span class=\"hljs-subst\">$&#123;result&#125;</span>|`</span>); <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//  |s t  r|</span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n\n","prev":{"title":" 4. html的元素有哪些（包含H5）？","slug":"interview/1d841137c9"},"next":{"title":" 7. HTML全局属性(global attribute)有哪些（包含H5）？","slug":"interview/09a7ebb8b8"},"categories":[{"name":"interview","slug":"interview","count":9,"path":"api/categories/interview.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"interview","slug":"interview","count":9,